\" custom_padding_phone=\"\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"3.25\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"3.25\" custom_padding=\"|||\" custom_padding__hover=\"|||\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.6.1\" text_font=\"Raleway||||||||\" text_font_size=\"18px\" text_line_height=\"1.6em\" text_orientation=\"center\" max_width=\"900px\" module_alignment=\"center\" text_font_size_tablet=\"\" text_font_size_phone=\"24px\" text_font_size_last_edited=\"on|phone\"]<p class=\"font_8\" style=\"text-align: left;\">We at Quokka believe that everyone deserves work happiness and an unbiased recruitment process. We are committed to helping our experts navigating through their work life and feeling fulfilled. Our platform helps experts find the job that fits their personality and professional goals. We believe in inputs = outputs, but there is no one formula that works for all. Create your formula. Pursue your career goals. Prioritize happiness. We think, happiness is when your inputs = your expected outputs.</p>\n<p class=\"font_8\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Quokka is a professional platform that helps experts find their work happiness by providing tools including job matching. Very often, our experts are following expectations put on them by society vs. what they really want. We believe that everyone has a unique core construct of who they are, what they want and what they are great at. Why not, find a job and company that fits your core construct. Companies have core constructs too, it is called leadership principles or core values. Companies look for experts that fit their core construct, why not find companies that fit yours. Imagine wearing a shoe that is too tight or too loose for a day, now imagine doing the same for a life time. Working a job that does not fit your core construct bruises and deteriorates your mental wellbeing and health in general. <span>An average person spends at least 40% of their waking hours at work (</span><span><a href=\"https://sloanreview.mit.edu/projects/measuring-culture-in-leading-companies/\" target=\"_blank\" data-content=\"https://sloanreview.mit.edu/projects/measuring-culture-in-leading-companies/\" data-type=\"external\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">source</a></span><span>). Studies show that X% of people are unhappy at work (source) and Y% surveyed are miserable. I</span><span>ndividuals that are happy lead happier lives, build stronger relationships, stay healthy, and live longer lives. [add stats, sources]. </span>Prioritize happiness. </p>\n<p class=\"font_8\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>Being good at your job doesn\'t always mean you are happy. [add supporting facts]</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>We believe that everyone deserves work happiness, it is not an option. F</span><span>ind your soul-job.</span></p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_text=\"Click here to join the happiest professional network today !\" button_alignment=\"center\" _builder_version=\"4.6.1\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"14px\" button_bg_color=\"#29cb8b\" button_border_width=\"12px\" button_border_color=\"#29cb8b\" button_letter_spacing=\"2px\" button_font=\"Poppins|600||on|||||\" button_icon=\"%%3%%\" background_layout=\"dark\" animation_style=\"slide\" animation_direction=\"top\" animation_intensity_slide=\"20%\" hover_enabled=\"0\" locked=\"off\" button_text_size__hover_enabled=\"off\" button_one_text_size__hover_enabled=\"off\" button_two_text_size__hover_enabled=\"off\" button_text_color__hover_enabled=\"off\" button_one_text_color__hover_enabled=\"off\" button_two_text_color__hover_enabled=\"off\" button_border_width__hover_enabled=\"off\" button_one_border_width__hover_enabled=\"off\" button_two_border_width__hover_enabled=\"off\" button_border_color__hover_enabled=\"off\" button_one_border_color__hover_enabled=\"off\" button_two_border_color__hover_enabled=\"off\" button_border_radius__hover_enabled=\"off\" button_one_border_radius__hover_enabled=\"o